{"tid":2133201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"單日149確診創新高 疫情處處燃燒  「漱口杯難救火」專家促封關","createTime":"2020-07-31T02:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T02:19:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5eb7ffe0925942e7ae547e470eb2dc7a8903d776","tid":2133201,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:19:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/E67672SHB4YCIVOPTXQF7ZTBTM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FE67672SHB4YCIVOPTXQF7ZTBTM%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG1wbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=1f338f07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FE67672SHB4YCIVOPTXQF7ZTBTM%2F&h=889e7c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/E67672SHB4YCIVOPTXQF7ZTBTM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n單日149確診創新高 疫情處處燃燒 <br />\n「漱口杯難救火」專家促封關<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】食衞局長陳肇始豪言本港疫情已見頂，言猶在耳，本港武肺確診個案昨即急升，新增149宗確診，其中145宗屬本地個案，兩個數字均創單日新高。本港累計3,152宗確診及疑似個案。另有73宗初步確診，其中三間醫院共四名病人初步確診需隔離。有專家形容疫情火頭處處，政府僅用「漱口杯救火」，促考慮封關。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ectvsuRsP7PHfx8Mm82omyoBNGA=/190x118/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZXKNBASHJ6GMGJ44Q3OW2GX2RQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FectvsuRsP7PHfx8Mm82omyoBNGA%3D%2F190x118%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZXKNBASHJ6GMGJ44Q3OW2GX2RQ.jpg&h=243bca46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本港疫情未見頂，昨再新增149宗確診個案，連續九日感染宗數逾百。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Pkg-3n1wkdHekVFKT4zmUmlgPiM=/640x800/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M756NGEBIMGIKO4SDQWWP22YZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPkg-3n1wkdHekVFKT4zmUmlgPiM%3D%2F640x800%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM756NGEBIMGIKO4SDQWWP22YZQ.jpg&h=62d538f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何栢良<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/O7DtBUVUnI38h-Sc6FupbzCnqYU=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GJYI63TGW3YZ6WOJQI2XHEN22Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FO7DtBUVUnI38h-Sc6FupbzCnqYU%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGJYI63TGW3YZ6WOJQI2XHEN22Q.jpg&h=bfba6399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伊利沙伯醫院分別有兩名病人入院後初步確診，有七名病人要隔離檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四醫院淪陷 病童恐播毒<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：市民嬲爆：當我哋馬騮咁玩<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總行政經理何婉霞透露，多間醫院有病人初步確診，其中伊利沙伯醫院一名64歲男病人7月28日因心臟問題入住內科病房，因白血球偏低，前日轉入監察病房及檢測，晚上初步確診，同病格有八名病人列為密切接觸者，其中一人已出院，餘下七人要隔離，無醫護列為密切接觸者；該院另一名71歲女病人亦因心臟問題前日入院，當時無發燒，情況穩定，由於病人胸口不適，入院三小時後轉入隔離病房檢測並初步確診，並無病人或醫護列為密切接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n北區醫院一名70歲女病人因疲倦乏力，前。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另明愛醫院一名四歲男童前日因發燒及嘔吐，入住監察病房及檢測，當晚初步確診後轉送瑪嘉烈醫院隔離治療。病人在明愛醫院。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於瑪嘉烈醫院四名支援服務員初步確診，。。。<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，新城電台群組再多一人初步確診，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良認為，每日過百宗確診個案，很多問題要處理，。。。。。。。。。。促請政府果斷進一步收緊邊境措施，包括考慮封關，亦要短期內叫停外傭來港。"},{"pid":"a7da77fa8920f2a504335f0606fc203a3a505057","tid":2133201,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:19:26.000Z","msg":"轉家食屎啦"},{"pid":"2a243c831c14d26b7c7649982f59dbe7b8e873d7","tid":2133201,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7da77fa8920f2a504335f0606fc203a3a505057","tid":2133201,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:19:26.000Z","msg":"轉家食屎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:19:37.000Z","msg":"專"}]}